==Nga ha Makwareala==
Shayandima ndi muḓi uno wanala tshipembe-vhukovhela ha [[Thohoyanḓou]]. Shayandima a si kule na Thohoyanḓou lune muthu anga tshimbila nga milenzhe u bva Shayandima uya Thohoyanḓou. Ḓorobo khulwane dza tsini ndi [[Thohoyandou]], [[Sibasa]] na [[Louis Trichardt]].

==Pfudzo==
Gudedzi la Tshidzini ḽi wanala henefha Shayandima. Gudedzi ili ndi la ugudisa vhathu mushumo wa vhunese. Gudedzi ili ḽi wanala tsini na vhuongelo ha [[Tshilidzini]].

==Vhadzulapo==
Vhunzhi ha vhathu vha no dzula afha vha amba tshiVenda.

==Mishumo==
Ha-Ramasaga (Shayandima Industrial Site) ndi hune vhathu vhanzhi vha Shayandima vha shuma hone. Vhaṅwe vha vhathu vha Shayandima vha shuma Thohoyanḓou.
